Method Detail

equals

public static boolean equals(Object a,
                             Object b)
Compares for equality, equating null with null, and treating Number instances almost mathematically.

Algorithm:

  1. If one argument is null, the other must be null too.
  2. If both are integral (Byte, Short, Integer, Long), exact mathematical equality.
  3. If both are numeric (integral or Float, Double), approximate double-equality.
  4. normal Object.equals(..)

equalSets

Are two collections equal as sets? Copes with null.

Checks whether a collection contains an element, based on Equals.equals. Iterates over the collection.
